4 FOR the purpose of altering the membership of the Commission on Behavioral Health Care
5 Treatment and Access; requiring the Commission to establish a workgroup on the
6 improvement of health, social, and economic outcomes related to substance use; and
7 generally relating to the Commission on Behavioral Health Care Treatment and
8 Access.
